  <ExtendedSection language="en">
    <Title><![CDATA[Usage of the common element settings]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links>
          <link name="link0" internal="true" type="A">
            <target><![CDATA[/sites/docu/opencms-documentation/todo/demos/common-element-settings/]]></target>
            <uuid>edf2ab69-d1cc-11ec-9238-0242ac11002b</uuid>
          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Now the element setting can be used in the tab "Supported settings" of any formatter configuration simply by using the <code>Setting name</code>. Remember to link to the configuration file to make the default element settings available.</p>
<div class="alert alert-info">Note: The other fields are not required, unless you want to change the default values as shown in the <a href="%(link0)">demo</a>.</div>]]></content>
      </Text>
    </Section>
