          </link>
        </links>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Now the configured element setting is available in the "Element settings" window, which you can open at the gear wheel <img style="width: 14px;" title="propertyBigIconActive" src="%(link0)" alt="" />, which appears when you hover over the edit point <img style="width: 14px;" title="backBigIconDeactivated" src="%(link1)" alt="" />.</p>]]></content>
